cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.HC 

The paper is about developing and validating deep learning algorithms for automated detection of critical findings in head CT scans. This involves image analysis and classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper also has implications for healthcare technology and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
